      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<script>\n// Run only on the specific page\nif (window.location.pathname.includes('/collections/hair-care')) {\n  document.write(`\n<section class=\"haircare-section\">\n  <h1>Trusted Hair Care Treatments in the UK</h1>\n  <p>Explore specialist solutions for healthier hair — including <strong>Finasteride</strong>, <strong>Minoxidil</strong>, <strong>Hair Growth Vitamins</strong>, and advanced <strong>Scalp Therapy</strong> treatments. All sourced from UK-registered pharmacies and delivered discreetly.</p>\n\n  <!-- Product Cards -->\n  <div class=\"haircare-cards\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h3>🧴 <strong>Finasteride</strong> (1 mg)</h3>\n      <p>A clinically proven oral treatment for male pattern hair loss — helps slow hair fall and stimulate new growth.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h3>🧴 <strong>Minoxidil</strong> (Topical Foam/Liquid)</h3>\n      <p>A trusted topical solution that enhances blood flow to the scalp and supports hair regrowth for many users.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h3>🧴 <strong>Hair Growth Vitamins</strong></h3>\n      <p>Essential nutrient formula-designed supplements to support hair health, strength and thickness — complementing treatments.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <h3>🧴 <strong>Scalp Therapy Kits</strong></h3>\n      <p>Advanced multi-step kits including serums, rollers & lasers to care for your scalp and boost treatment effectiveness.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Table Section -->\n  <div class=\"table-section\">\n     <h2><b>Compare Our Top Hair Care Treatments</h2>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Treatment</th>\n          <th>Method</th>\n          <th>Results Timeline</th>\n          <th>Common Side-Effects</th>\n          <th>Recommended For</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td data-label=\"Treatment\">Finasteride</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Method\">Oral daily tablet</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Results Timeline\">3-6 months visible improvement</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Common Side-Effects\">Reduced libido, mild dizziness</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Recommended For\">Men with early-stage hair loss</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td data-label=\"Treatment\">Minoxidil</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Method\">Topical foam/liquid application</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Results Timeline\">2-4 months to see regrowth</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Common Side-Effects\">Scalp irritation, shedding phase</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Recommended For\">Men & women seeking thicker hair</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td data-label=\"Treatment\">Hair Growth Vitamins</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Method\">Oral supplement</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Results Timeline\">4-8 weeks improved texture</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Common Side-Effects\">Rare mild digestive upset</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Recommended For\">Those with nutrient-deficient hair</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td data-label=\"Treatment\">Scalp Therapy Kits</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Method\">Multi-step topical & device kit</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Results Timeline\">6-12 weeks enhanced uptake</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Common Side-Effects\">Initial tingling, device costs</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Recommended For\">Advanced users seeking full regimen</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ Section -->\n  <div class=\"faq\"><b>\n\n    <b><h2><b>Frequently Asked Questions About Hair Loss & Treatment</h2><b>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>What causes hair loss in men and women?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Hair loss can be driven by genetics, hormonal changes, nutritional deficiencies, stress, or scalp conditions. Identifying the root cause is key to effective treatment.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>How soon will I see results from hair loss treatments?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Most users see reduced shedding in 2-3 months, and visible regrowth by 4-6 months. Consistency is vital.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Are hair-loss pills safe?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">When prescribed by a healthcare professional and from a licensed UK pharmacy, they are considered safe. Always review your health status first.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Does Minoxidil or Finasteride work better?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">They work differently. Finasteride addresses hormonal causes; Minoxidil supports circulation. Many users combine them under medical advice.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Can vitamins alone stop hair loss?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Vitamins support hair health but rarely stop hair loss alone unless deficiency is the main cause. They’re best used alongside treatments.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Is hair-regrowth permanent?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Results can last as long as treatment continues. Stopping treatments often leads to resumed shedding within months.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Can lifestyle changes help hair loss?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes — improving nutrition, reducing stress, getting better sleep and treating scalp conditions all support stronger hair and better treatment outcomes.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- FIXED: corrected div class here so theme & JS apply -->\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Will hair-loss treatments work for women too?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Many do. Treatments such as Minoxidil and nutritional support are indicated for women — but always under appropriate supervision.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>What side-effects should I expect?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Mild scalp irritation (topical), initial shedding phase, hormonal changes (oral). Serious effects are rare but always consult your doctor.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Where can I buy genuine hair-loss treatments online?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Only buy from regulated UK pharmacies like Pharmazon Express to ensure authenticity, safe delivery and pharmacist support.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CTA Section -->\n  <div class=\"cta-box\">\n    <h2>Start Your Hair Renewal Journey Today</h2>\n    <p>Discover our complete range of hair-care treatments — genuine, effective, and discreetly delivered across the UK.</p>\n    <a href=\"/collections/hair-care\" class=\"cta-btn\">Explore Hair Care Treatments</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n  `);\n\n  // Add CSS dynamically\n  const style = document.createElement('style');\n  style.textContent = `\n  .haircare-section {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 100%);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 40px 20px;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    color: #1e293b;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: 40px auto;\n  }\n  .haircare-section h1 {\n    font-size: 32px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg,#4c3e79,#4c3e79);\n    -webkit-background-clip:text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;\n  }\n  .haircare-section h2 { font-size:24px; text-align:center; margin:40px 0 15px;}\n  .haircare-section h3 { font-size:20px; color:#4c3e79; margin-bottom:10px; text-align:center;}\n  .haircare-section p { font-size:16px; text-align:center; margin-bottom:20px;}\n\n  .haircare-cards { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:25px; justify-items:center; margin-top:30px;}\n  .card { background:#fff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:16px; padding:25px; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box; transition:all 0.3s;}\n  .card:hover { box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(37,99,235,0.15); transform:translateY(-3px);}\n  .card p { font-size:16px; color:#475569;}\n  .card p strong { font-weight:bold;}\n\n  .table-section { margin-top:40px; overflow-x:auto;}\n  .table-section table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:14px; border:2px solid #e2e8f0;}\n  .table-section th, .table-section td { border:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:12px;}\n  .table-section th { background:#f1f5f9; font-weight:600; color:#0f172a;}\n  .table-section tr:nth-child(even){ background:#f9fafb;}\n\n  .faq { margin-top:40px;}\n  .faq-item { background:#f8fafc; border-radius:10px; padding:15px 20px; margin-bottom:10px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; cursor:pointer; transition:0.3s; position:relative;}\n  .faq-item:hover { background:#f1f5f9;}\n  .faq-item h4 { margin:0; font-size:16px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;}\n  .faq-item h4::after { content:'+'; font-weight:bold; font-size:18px; transition: transform 0.3s;}\n  .faq-item.active h4::after { content:'−'; transform:rotate(180deg);}\n  .faq-answer { max-height:0; overflow:hidden; font-size:15px; color:#475569; margin-top:10px; line-height:1.6; transition:max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.3s ease;}\n\n  .cta-box { text-align:center; margin-top:50px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#705f9d,#e1ceff); color:#fff; padding:40px 20px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);}\n  .cta-box h2 { font-size:24px; margin-bottom:10px; color:#fff; font-weight:700;}\n  .cta-box p { font-size:16px; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:25px;}\n  .cta-btn { background:#fff; color:#000000; padding:12px 28px; border-radius:30px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; transition:0.3s;}\n  .cta-btn:hover { background:#e0f2fe;}\n\n  @media(max-width:1024px){ .haircare-cards { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:20px;} }\n  @media(max-width:768px){\n    .haircare-section h1{font-size:28px;}\n    .haircare-section h2{font-size:22px;}\n    .haircare-section h3{font-size:18px;}\n    .haircare-section p{font-size:15px;}\n    .cta-box h2{font-size:20px;}\n    .cta-box p{font-size:14px;}\n    .table-section table, .table-section thead, .table-section tbody, .table-section th, .table-section td, .table-section tr { display:block;}\n    .table-section thead tr { display:none;}\n    .table-section tr { margin-bottom:15px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:10px;}\n    .table-section td { border:none; padding:5px 10px; position:relative; text-align:left;}\n    .table-section td::before { content: attr(data-label); font-weight:600; display:inline-block; width:120px; color:#0f172a;}\n  }\n  `;\n  document.head.appendChild(style);\n  \n  // FAQ toggle\n  document.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    if (e.target.closest('.faq-item')) {\n      const item = e.target.closest('.faq-item');\n      const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');\n      if (item.classList.contains('active')) {\n        answer.style.maxHeight = null;\n        item.classList.remove('active');\n      } else {\n        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item.active').forEach(activeItem => {\n          activeItem.querySelector('.faq-answer').style.maxHeight = null;\n          activeItem.classList.remove('active');\n        });\n        answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + 'px';\n        item.classList.add('active');\n      }\n    }\n  });\n}\n</script>",
