     <h4>Are ED tablets safe?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, when prescribed and taken correctly from licensed pharmacies like Pharmazon Express.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Can I buy ED medicines online in the UK?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, as long as it’s a registered UK pharmacy. Pharmazon Express ensures genuine and discreet delivery.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>How quickly does Viagra work?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Usually within 30–60 minutes after taking. It’s best taken on an empty stomach for faster effect.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Does Cialis really last 36 hours?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, <strong>Cialis</strong> offers extended duration — ideal for spontaneous intimacy throughout the weekend.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Can ED tablets be taken daily?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Some low-dose versions like <strong>Cialis Daily</strong> can be taken every day. Always follow medical advice.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Are there side effects?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Mild headache, flushing, or dizziness can occur but are usually temporary and fade quickly.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>Can I drink alcohol with ED medication?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Moderate alcohol is fine, but too much can lower performance and reduce medicine effectiveness.</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h4>What if ED medication doesn’t work?</h4>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Consult your doctor. A different dose or treatment type may be more effective for you.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CTA Section -->\n  <div class=\"cta-box\">\n    <h2>Start Your Confidence Journey Today</h2>\n    <p>Regain control with proven <strong>ED treatments</strong> like <strong>Via